    @Deprecated(since="2021-05-27")
public static interface Authentication.NonAuthenticated
extends Authentication.LoginAuthentication
    Deprecated.
    The Eclipse Jetty and Apache Felix Http Jetty packages are no longer supported.
    After a logout, the authentication reverts to a state where it is possible to programmatically log in again.
